---
title: Almond-Crusted Pork & Butter Roast Veggies with Brussels Sprouts & Italian Truffle Mayo
description: There are two sure-fire ways to jazz up any dinner and that’s a gorgeous crumbing moment and a good sauce.
That’s how this pork dinner went from five stars, with almond crusting on the pork and a Truffle mayo. It’s fine dining without the fuss or price tag.
